# Plans

When creating a plan using the CreatePlan tool, it may be saved to the Cursor-level directory (`~/.cursor/plans/`) rather than the workspace. Always ensure plan files end up in the workspace at `.cursor/plans/` so they are committed to the repo.

After creating a plan, verify the file exists at `.cursor/plans/<name>.plan.md` in the workspace. If it was saved elsewhere, copy it to the workspace plans directory.
